Inter - Continental Hotels plans hotels in Brazil . Inter - Continental Hotels and Resorts said Monday its Americas division had a joint venture agreement with Brazilian developer Brascan Imobilaria S . A . to build and manage 12 Inter - Continental or Forum brand hotels in Brazil by 2000 . Inter - Continental is a unit of privately - held Saison Group , an investor group based in Japan . The two companies first formed a joint venture to build the Hotel Inter - Continental Rio and the newly - opened Hotel Inter - Continental Sao Paolo . Inter - Continental , which owns over 195 hotels in 69 countries , said it was trying to increase its Forum brand and its Resort portfolio in Latin America . 
